A = incoming data rate of the real time stream 
       
B= outgoing data rate of the radio link 
                               For IPv6 
    
       
T1 = (A*T(0))/B 
       
T2 = (A*T(1))/B = (A*((A*T(0))/B))/B = ((A/B)**2)*T(0) 
       
                        ... 
       
R = limit (n->infinity) sum (i = 0,n) ((A/B)**i)*T(0) 
    
R = T(0)/(1 - (A/B)) 
    
